# Phase 4.3: Performance Optimization (PWA Focus - Initial)

## Lighthouse Performance Audit

- [ ] Run Lighthouse "Performance" audit
  - Use Chrome DevTools on deployed PWA
  - Compare and improve score from previous audits
  - Document key metrics and areas for improvement

## Image Optimization

- [ ] Next.js Image Component Implementation
  - Verify usage of Next.js <Image> component for all images
  - Check implementation for video thumbnails
  - Ensure proper lazy loading behavior

- [ ] Image Configuration
  - Configure sizes prop for responsive images
  - Set priority prop for critical images (e.g., first video thumbnail)
  - Verify proper image formats and compression

## Code Splitting & Lazy Loading

- [ ] Bundle Size Analysis
  - Review Next.js automatic code splitting
  - Use Next.js DevTools or Webpack Bundle Analyzer
  - Identify and optimize large bundles
  - Document any bundle size concerns

## Video Optimization

- [ ] Video Encoding Standards
  - Verify test videos use MP4 format
  - Check H.264 codec implementation
  - Ensure reasonable bitrate/resolution
  - Test video loading performance on mobile networks

- [ ] Firebase Storage Configuration
  - Review video upload settings
  - Verify proper caching headers
  - Test video delivery performance 